  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/68c2d8df396773c743c896722f7cd32e.poster.avif?t=1656032520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/68c2d8df396773c743c896722f7cd32e.webm?t=1656032520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/68c2d8df396773c743c896722f7cd32e.mp4?t=1656032520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Royale Age is the first ever attempt to combine Battle Royale and Auto Chess into a new refreshing game that highlights your skill and strategy thinking.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR ARMY</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/ad476dd118befe8d831cee8a3abb3149.avif?t=1656032520\" width=597 height=197 /></span><br>Select from the variety of units that are available and build a personalized army in your style!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/c5e5cc17ea484f25aa03dd83d72a1398.poster.avif?t=1656032520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/c5e5cc17ea484f25aa03dd83d72a1398.webm?t=1656032520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/c5e5cc17ea484f25aa03dd83d72a1398.mp4?t=1656032520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMPETE WITH OTHER KINGS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/b49ba0fb865d4291be6c8a3e68c4bc65.avif?t=1656032520\" width=597 height=197 /></span><br>Prove your worth as the best King by competing in the ranked ladder and win several prizes!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVEL UP YOUR KINGDOM</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/909a4d637046a6b2bf03c7d72368c574.poster.avif?t=1656032520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/909a4d637046a6b2bf03c7d72368c574.webm?t=1656032520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/909a4d637046a6b2bf03c7d72368c574.mp4?t=1656032520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enrich your people once again and show them you were not poor all along!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNCOVER HIDDEN CHALLENGES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208540/extras/48080aa35f069cb1efef094c4dd38c7f.avif?t=1656032520\" width=597 height=197 /></span><br>Find all the secret achievements and earn lots of prizes!",
